claim: Vince Vaughn appeared in the 1993 sports film Rudy.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He has appeared in a number of films in the 1990s , including the sports film Rudy  (  1993  )  , the sci-fi adventure dinosaur film The Lost World : Jurassic Park  (  1997  )  , and the drama-thriller Return to Paradise  (  1998  )  .
